KEINEMOD-MANIPULATE_HISTORY.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold]{IfUpgraded:show: up to|} {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: [gold]Create[/gold] a [gold]{IfUpgraded:show:Scroll of Valor+|Scroll of Valor}[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-RESHAPE_HISTORY.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
Draw {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Choose {IfUpgraded:show:an [gold]Upgraded[/gold]|a} [gold]Sacred Treasure[/gold] to [gold]Create[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-SLAY_THE_SERPENT.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] 1 card, if it is [gold]Snakebite[/gold] or [gold]Serpent Form[/gold], [gold]Create[/gold] a [gold]{IfUpgraded:show:Heavenly Sword+|Heavenly Sword}[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: [gold]Create[/gold] a [gold]{IfUpgraded:show:Serpent Form|Snakebite}[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-MASAKADO_CRISIS.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}, [gold]Time Shift[/gold] {TimeShiftPower:diff()} for each.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Gain {Energy:energyIcons()}, [gold]Recall[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}, gain 1 less {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} for each.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-YOSHIMITSU_CRISIS.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}, gain {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} for each.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: [gold]Recall[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}, gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold] for each.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-PHASE_STRIKE.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Time Shift[/gold] {TimeShiftPower:diff()}.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Gain {Energy:energyIcons()}, exit your form.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-CONCEAL.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
Apply {HistoricalGapPower:diff()} [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Block[/gold] is retained for a turn.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Enemy's [gold]Historical Gap[/gold] does not decay for a turn.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-SCROLL_SLASH.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage to ALL enemies.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: Next turn, gain {Energy:energyIcons()}.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Draw {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-SCROLL_STORM.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage {Repeat:diff()} times.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: Gain {KnowledgePower:diff()} [gold]Knowledge[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Hits {RepeatExtra:diff()} additional time.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-UNOFFICIAL_HISTORY.description:
Apply {HistoricalGapPower:diff()} [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].
Gain {WeakGain:diff()} [gold]Weak[/gold].
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: Apply {WeakPower:diff()} [gold]Weak[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Does not gains [gold]Weak[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-LEARN_FROM_PAIN.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage {Repeat:cond:>1?{} times|}.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] 1 card, if it is a Status or Curse, gain {KnowledgePower:diff()} [gold]Knowledge[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Hits {RepeatExtra:diff()} additional time.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-FEAST_OF_HISTORY.description:
Apply {HistoricalGapPower:diff()} [gold]Historical Gap[/gold] to ALL enemies {Times:diff()} {Times:plural:time|times}.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] your [gold]Hand[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Apply {TimesExtra:diff()} additional times.{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-SIDES_OF_THE_MOON.description:
Apply {Gap:diff()} [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Time Shift[/gold] equal to half of enemy's [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Apply {GapExtra:diff()} additional [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-WORKFLOW.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] 1 card, if it is a [gold]Sacred Scroll[/gold], [gold]Create[/gold] 1 [gold]Flow[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: [gold]Create[/gold] a [gold]Scroll of Wisdom[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-WIPED_FROM_HISTORY.description:
Deal {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: Gain [gold]Block[/gold] equal to enemy's [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: Deal additional damage equal to double enemy's [gold]Historical Gap[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-GUIDANCE.description:
Choose another player, whenever you [gold]Consume[/gold] a Non-[gold]Unplayable[/gold] card this turn, they get a copy of it.
Draw {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.{HumanSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-AMATERASU.description:
Deal {CalculatedDamage:diff()} damage to ALL enemies.
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: Gain {ValorPower:diff()} [gold]Valor[/gold].{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: This card's damage scales with your [gold]Valor[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-DETERMINATION.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
Gain {ValorPower:diff()} [gold]Valor[/gold].
{HumanSec}{HumanOpen}Human{HumanClose}: [gold]Consume[/gold] up to {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards}.{HumanSecEnd}
{HakuSec}{HakuOpen}Hakutaku{HakuClose}: [gold]Upgrade[/gold] {Cards:diff()} {Cards:plural:card|cards} in your [gold]Hand[/gold].{HakuSecEnd}

KEINEMOD-REINCARNATION.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage. If [gold]Fatal[/gold], permanently increase damage by {Increment:diff()}. If kills a Boss, capture its [gold]Reincarnation[/gold].
At the start of each combat, [gold]Create[/gold] a [gold]Returning Bridge[/gold] if this has captured [gold]Reincarnation[/gold].{SlayedBosses.StringValue:cond:
(Captured: {}.)|}

KEINEMOD-DETACHMENT.description:
[gold]Exhaust[/gold] your [gold]Scroll[/gold].
For every {Ratio:diff()} cards [gold]Exhausted[/gold], gain {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)} and draw 1 card.{InCombat:
(Gain {CalculatedCount:diff()} {energyPrefix:energyIcons(1)}, draw {CalculatedCount:diff()} {CalculatedCount:plural:card|cards})|}
